{
  "video_id": "xlUPlxSpDRo",
  "title": "Stories from a home for terminally ill children | Kathy Hull",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12660.0,
      "end_time": 17276.0,
      "text": "I want to introduce you to some very wise kids that I&#39;ve known,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 17300.0,
      "end_time": 19740.0,
      "text": "but first I want to introduce you to a camel."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 20540.0,
      "end_time": 24796.0,
      "text": "This is Cassie, a therapy camel visiting one of our young patients"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 24820.0,
      "end_time": 26200.0,
      "text": "in her room,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 26740.0,
      "end_time": 28990.0,
      "text": "which is pretty magical."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 29700.0,
      "end_time": 34379.0,
      "text": "A friend of mine raises camels at his ranch in the Santa Cruz Mountains."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 34860.0,
      "end_time": 36516.0,
      "text": "He has about eight of them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 36540.0,
      "end_time": 38236.0,
      "text": "and he started 30 years ago"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 38260.0,
      "end_time": 40379.0,
      "text": "because he thought horses were too mundane."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 41220.0,
      "end_time": 44596.0,
      "text": "John is an out-of-the-box thinker,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 44620.0,
      "end_time": 47436.0,
      "text": "which explains why the two of us have been such good friends"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 47460.0,
      "end_time": 48660.0,
      "text": "all of our lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 50200.0,
      "end_time": 55156.0,
      "text": "Over the years, I&#39;ve convinced him to shuttle those sweet furry beasts"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 55180.0,
      "end_time": 58140.0,
      "text": "up to hang out with our sick kids from time to time."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 59260.0,
      "end_time": 61675.0,
      "text": "Talking to John, I was surprised to learn"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 61700.0,
      "end_time": 66900.0,
      "text": "that camels have an average life expectancy of 40 to 50 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 67420.0,
      "end_time": 70916.0,
      "text": "The life expectancy of many of the children with whom I work"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 70940.0,
      "end_time": 72259.0,
      "text": "is less than a year."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 73340.0,
      "end_time": 76395.0,
      "text": "This is a picture of the George Mark Children&#39;s House,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 76419.0,
      "end_time": 79916.0,
      "text": "the first pediatric palliative respite care center"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 79940.0,
      "end_time": 82196.0,
      "text": "to open in the United States."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 82220.0,
      "end_time": 85196.0,
      "text": "I founded it in 2004,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 85220.0,
      "end_time": 88156.0,
      "text": "after years of working as a psychologist"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 88180.0,
      "end_time": 90876.0,
      "text": "on pediatric intensive care units,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 90900.0,
      "end_time": 95916.0,
      "text": "frustrated with the undignified deaths that so many children experienced"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 95940.0,
      "end_time": 97860.0,
      "text": "and their families had to endure."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 98780.0,
      "end_time": 102956.0,
      "text": "As I sat with families whose children were at the end of their lives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 102980.0,
      "end_time": 106636.0,
      "text": "I was acutely aware of our surroundings."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 106660.0,
      "end_time": 110676.0,
      "text": "While the elevated train rumbled overhead on its track,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 110700.0,
      "end_time": 115460.0,
      "text": "quite literally the room reverberated with each passing train car."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 116300.0,
      "end_time": 119676.0,
      "text": "The lights on the ward were fluorescent and too bright."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 119700.0,
      "end_time": 122916.0,
      "text": "Monitors beeped, as did the elevator,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 122940.0,
      "end_time": 124940.0,
      "text": "noisily announcing its arrival."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 125700.0,
      "end_time": 127676.0,
      "text": "These families were experiencing"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 127700.0,
      "end_time": 131316.0,
      "text": "some of the most excruciating moments of their lives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 131340.0,
      "end_time": 134916.0,
      "text": "and I so wanted them to have a more peaceful place"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 134940.0,
      "end_time": 138500.0,
      "text": "in which to say a last goodbye to their young daughters and sons."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 139300.0,
      "end_time": 140940.0,
      "text": "Surely, I thought,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 141780.0,
      "end_time": 145396.0,
      "text": "there must be a better spot than a hospital intensive care unit"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 145420.0,
      "end_time": 147619.0,
      "text": "for children at the end of their lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 148540.0,
      "end_time": 150140.0,
      "text": "Our children&#39;s house"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 151340.0,
      "end_time": 153340.0,
      "text": "is calm and nurturing."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 153860.0,
      "end_time": 156476.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a place where families can stay together"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 156500.0,
      "end_time": 159760.0,
      "text": "to enjoy quality time with their children,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 159100.0,
      "end_time": 161835.0,
      "text": "many of whom are there for respite stays,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 161860.0,
      "end_time": 165396.0,
      "text": "some with repeated visits over a span of many years."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 165420.0,
      "end_time": 167980.0,
      "text": "We call those kids our frequent flyers."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 170180.0,
      "end_time": 173596.0,
      "text": "Rather than the bright, noisy quarters of the hospital,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 173620.0,
      "end_time": 176436.0,
      "text": "their rooms are calm and comfortable,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 176460.0,
      "end_time": 179716.0,
      "text": "with actual living spaces for the families,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 179740.0,
      "end_time": 181516.0,
      "text": "a sanctuary of gardens"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 181540.0,
      "end_time": 184360.0,
      "text": "and a wonderful outdoor playground"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 184600.0,
      "end_time": 187580.0,
      "text": "with special structures for children with physical limitations."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 188860.0,
      "end_time": 191196.0,
      "text": "This sweet baby Lars"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 191220.0,
      "end_time": 195180.0,
      "text": "came to us directly from a hospital intensive care unit."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 196260.0,
      "end_time": 199396.0,
      "text": "Imagine hearing the heartbreaking news"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 199420.0,
      "end_time": 201579.0,
      "text": "that none of us would ever want to hear."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 202180.0,
      "end_time": 205916.0,
      "text": "His parents had been told that Lars had a brain anomaly"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 205940.0,
      "end_time": 208756.0,
      "text": "that would keep him from ever swallowing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 208780.0,
      "end_time": 210676.0,
      "text": "walking, talking"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 210700.0,
      "end_time": 212380.0,
      "text": "or developing mentally."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 213300.0,
      "end_time": 216276.0,
      "text": "Recognizing what little chance he had for survival,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 216300.0,
      "end_time": 219356.0,
      "text": "his parents chose to focus on the quality of time"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 219380.0,
      "end_time": 220859.0,
      "text": "that they could spend together."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 221420.0,
      "end_time": 223995.0,
      "text": "They moved into one of our family apartments"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 224200.0,
      "end_time": 226436.0,
      "text": "and treasured each day that they had,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 226460.0,
      "end_time": 227940.0,
      "text": "which were far too few."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 228820.0,
      "end_time": 231676.0,
      "text": "Lars&#39;s life was brief, to be sure,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 231700.0,
      "end_time": 233316.0,
      "text": "mere weeks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 233340.0,
      "end_time": 235876.0,
      "text": "but it was calm and comfortable."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 235900.0,
      "end_time": 238100.0,
      "text": "He went on hikes with his parents."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 238740.0,
      "end_time": 241716.0,
      "text": "The time that he spent in the pool with our aquatic therapist"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 241740.0,
      "end_time": 243916.0,
      "text": "lessened the seizures he was experiencing"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 243940.0,
      "end_time": 245620.0,
      "text": "and helped him to sleep at night."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 246140.0,
      "end_time": 248196.0,
      "text": "His family had a peaceful place"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 248220.0,
      "end_time": 250596.0,
      "text": "in which to both celebrate his life"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 250620.0,
      "end_time": 252600.0,
      "text": "and mourn his death."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 252860.0,
      "end_time": 256760.0,
      "text": "It has been five years since Lars was with us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 256100.00000000003,
      "end_time": 257996.00000000003,
      "text": "and in that time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 258190.0,
      "end_time": 260356.0,
      "text": "his family has welcomed"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 260380.0,
      "end_time": 262540.0,
      "text": "a daughter and another son."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 263100.0,
      "end_time": 266360.0,
      "text": "They are such a powerful testament"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 266600.0,
      "end_time": 270219.0,
      "text": "to the positive outcome that specialized children&#39;s hospice care can create."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 271460.0,
      "end_time": 274116.0,
      "text": "Their baby&#39;s physical discomfort was well managed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 274140.0,
      "end_time": 278900.0,
      "text": "giving all of them the gift of time to be together in a beautiful place."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 280100.0,
      "end_time": 282116.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m going to talk to you now"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 282140.0,
      "end_time": 283356.0,
      "text": "about the elephant"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 283380.0,
      "end_time": 285140.0,
      "text": "rather than the camel in the room."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 287260.0,
      "end_time": 290396.0,
      "text": "Very few people want to talk about death,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 290420.0,
      "end_time": 293940.0,
      "text": "and even fewer about children&#39;s death."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 297500.0,
      "end_time": 299600.0,
      "text": "Loss of a child,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 299900.0,
      "end_time": 302476.0,
      "text": "especially for those of us who have our own children,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 302500.0,
      "end_time": 303700.0,
      "text": "is frightening,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 304620.0,
      "end_time": 305820.0,
      "text": "more than frightening,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 306660.0,
      "end_time": 307860.0,
      "text": "paralyzing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 308740.0,
      "end_time": 309940.0,
      "text": "debilitating,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 310740.0,
      "end_time": 311940.0,
      "text": "impossible."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 313140.0,
      "end_time": 315395.0,
      "text": "But what I&#39;ve learned is this:"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 315420.0,
      "end_time": 317436.0,
      "text": "children don&#39;t stop dying"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 317460.0,
      "end_time": 319436.0,
      "text": "just because we the adults"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 319460.0,
      "end_time": 322140.0,
      "text": "can&#39;t comprehend the injustice of losing them."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 322820.0,
      "end_time": 324990.0,
      "text": "And what&#39;s more,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 325340.0,
      "end_time": 327116.0,
      "text": "if we can be brave enough"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 327140.0,
      "end_time": 328996.0,
      "text": "to face the possibility of death,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 329200.0,
      "end_time": 330940.0,
      "text": "even among the most innocent,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 331940.0,
      "end_time": 334620.0,
      "text": "we gain an unparalleled kind of wisdom."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 336600.0,
      "end_time": 337660.0,
      "text": "Take Crystal, for example."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 339380.0,
      "end_time": 341756.0,
      "text": "She was one of the first children to come for care"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 341780.0,
      "end_time": 343179.0,
      "text": "after we opened our doors."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 344100.0,
      "end_time": 345756.0,
      "text": "She was nine when she arrived,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 345780.0,
      "end_time": 350116.0,
      "text": "and her neurologist expected that she might live another two weeks."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 350140.0,
      "end_time": 352635.0,
      "text": "She had an inoperable brain tumor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 352660.0,
      "end_time": 355396.0,
      "text": "and her decline had really accelerated"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 355420.0,
      "end_time": 357340.0,
      "text": "in the week before she came to us."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 358600.0,
      "end_time": 360360.0,
      "text": "After settling into her room,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 360600.0,
      "end_time": 363796.0,
      "text": "dressed entirely in pink and lavender,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 363820.0,
      "end_time": 367916.0,
      "text": "surrounded by the Hello Kitty accessories that she loved,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 367940.0,
      "end_time": 370676.0,
      "text": "she spent the next several days"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 370700.0,
      "end_time": 373260.0,
      "text": "winning over the hearts of every staff member."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 374580.0,
      "end_time": 377756.0,
      "text": "Bit by bit, her condition stabilized,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 377780.0,
      "end_time": 380195.0,
      "text": "and then to our astonishment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 380220.0,
      "end_time": 381860.0,
      "text": "she actually improved."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 382980.0,
      "end_time": 384636.0,
      "text": "There were a variety of factors"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 384660.0,
      "end_time": 388236.0,
      "text": "that contributed to Crystal&#39;s improvement"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 388260.0,
      "end_time": 391820.0,
      "text": "which we later came to call the \"George Mark bump,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 392940.0,
      "end_time": 395796.0,
      "text": "a lovely, not uncommon phenomenon"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 395820.0,
      "end_time": 398716.0,
      "text": "where children outlive the prognoses of their illnesses"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 398740.0,
      "end_time": 400420.0,
      "text": "if they&#39;re outside of the hospital."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 402100.0,
      "end_time": 405540.0,
      "text": "The calmer atmosphere of her surroundings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 406340.0,
      "end_time": 411155.0,
      "text": "tasty meals that were fixed often to accommodate her requests,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 411180.0,
      "end_time": 412860.0,
      "text": "the resident pets,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 413460.0,
      "end_time": 417700.0,
      "text": "the therapy dog and rabbit spent lots of cozy time with Crystal."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 418980.0,
      "end_time": 421916.0,
      "text": "After she had been with us for about a week,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 421940.0,
      "end_time": 423836.0,
      "text": "she called her grandmother,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 423860.0,
      "end_time": 425276.0,
      "text": "and she said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 425300.0,
      "end_time": 428916.0,
      "text": "\"Gee, I&#39;m staying in a great big house,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 428940.0,
      "end_time": 431180.0,
      "text": "and there&#39;s room for you to come, too."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 431900.0,
      "end_time": 433556.0,
      "text": "And guess what?"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 433580.0,
      "end_time": 435596.0,
      "text": "You don&#39;t have to bring any quarters"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 435620.0,
      "end_time": 437876.0,
      "text": "because the washer and dryer are free.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 437900.0,
      "end_time": 440750.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 440100.0,
      "end_time": 442956.0,
      "text": "Crystal&#39;s grandmother soon arrived from out of town,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 442980.0,
      "end_time": 447516.0,
      "text": "and they spent the remaining four months of Crystal&#39;s life"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 447540.0,
      "end_time": 449996.0,
      "text": "enjoying very special days together."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 450200.0,
      "end_time": 453996.0,
      "text": "Some days were special because Crystal was outside in her wheelchair"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 454200.0,
      "end_time": 455299.0,
      "text": "sitting by the fountain."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 455860.0,
      "end_time": 460236.0,
      "text": "For a little girl who had spent most of the year earlier in a hospital bed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 460260.0,
      "end_time": 463195.0,
      "text": "being outside counting hummingbirds"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 463220.0,
      "end_time": 465556.0,
      "text": "made for an amazing time with her grandma,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 465580.0,
      "end_time": 466780.0,
      "text": "and lots of laughter."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 467460.0,
      "end_time": 469996.0,
      "text": "Other days were special because of the activities"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 470200.0,
      "end_time": 472859.0,
      "text": "that our child life specialist created for her."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 473660.0,
      "end_time": 477836.0,
      "text": "Crystal strung beads and made jewelry for everybody in the house."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 477860.0,
      "end_time": 481200.0,
      "text": "She painted a pumpkin to help decorate for Halloween."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 482180.0,
      "end_time": 486516.0,
      "text": "She spent many excited days planning her tenth birthday,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 486540.0,
      "end_time": 489260.0,
      "text": "which of course none of us thought she would ever see."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 490820.0,
      "end_time": 493956.0,
      "text": "All of us wore pink boas for the occasion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 493980.0,
      "end_time": 496516.0,
      "text": "and Crystal, as you can see,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 496540.0,
      "end_time": 497756.0,
      "text": "queen for a day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 497780.0,
      "end_time": 499299.0,
      "text": "wore a sparkly tiara."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 500460.0,
      "end_time": 502195.0,
      "text": "One hot morning, I arrived at work"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 502220.0,
      "end_time": 507716.0,
      "text": "and Crystal and her partner in crime, Charlie, greeted me."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 507740.0,
      "end_time": 510876.0,
      "text": "With some help, they had set up a lemonade and cookie stand"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 510900.0,
      "end_time": 512220.0,
      "text": "outside the front door,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 512820.00000000006,
      "end_time": 515600.00000000006,
      "text": "a very strategic location."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 517140.0,
      "end_time": 520515.0,
      "text": "I asked Crystal the price of the cookie that I had selected,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 520539.0,
      "end_time": 523750.0,
      "text": "and she said, \"Three dollars.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 523100.0,
      "end_time": 526955.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 526979.0,
      "end_time": 530760.0,
      "text": "I said that seemed a bit high for one cookie."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 530100.0,
      "end_time": 531835.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 531859.0,
      "end_time": 533600.0,
      "text": "It was small."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 535140.0,
      "end_time": 537836.0,
      "text": "\"I know,\" she acknowledged with a grin,"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 537860.0,
      "end_time": 539260.0,
      "text": "\"but I&#39;m worth it.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 540820.0,
      "end_time": 542716.0,
      "text": "And therein lie the words of wisdom"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 542740.0,
      "end_time": 547220.0,
      "text": "of a young girl whose brief life forever impacted mine."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 548620.0,
      "end_time": 550600.0,
      "text": "Crystal was worth it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 550900.0,
      "end_time": 556196.0,
      "text": "and shouldn&#39;t every child whose life is shortened by a horrific illness"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 556220.0,
      "end_time": 557420.0,
      "text": "be worth it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 557860.0,
      "end_time": 560760.0,
      "text": "Together, all of us today"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 560100.0,
      "end_time": 563356.0,
      "text": "can offer that same specialized care that Crystal received"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 563380.0,
      "end_time": 569360.0,
      "text": "by recognizing that children&#39;s respite and hospice care"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 569600.0,
      "end_time": 573420.0,
      "text": "is a critical component missing from our healthcare landscape."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 575375.0,
      "end_time": 576756.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s also interesting to note"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 576780.0,
      "end_time": 578596.0,
      "text": "that we are able to provide this care"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 578620.0,
      "end_time": 582300.0,
      "text": "at about one third of the cost of a hospital intensive care unit,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 583140.0,
      "end_time": 585980.0,
      "text": "and our families don&#39;t see a bill."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 586700.0,
      "end_time": 589476.0,
      "text": "We are ever grateful to the supporters"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 589500.0,
      "end_time": 591940.0,
      "text": "who believe in this important work that we&#39;re doing."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 593820.0,
      "end_time": 597276.0,
      "text": "The truth is that my colleagues and I"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 597300.0,
      "end_time": 600876.0,
      "text": "and the parents and other family members"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 600900.0,
      "end_time": 603876.0,
      "text": "who get to experience this special wisdom"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 603900.0,
      "end_time": 605660.0,
      "text": "are in a unique position."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 606700.0,
      "end_time": 611916.0,
      "text": "There are only two freestanding pediatric hospices in the United States,"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 611940.0,
      "end_time": 614636.0,
      "text": "although I&#39;m happy to report that based on our model,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 614660.0,
      "end_time": 618716.0,
      "text": "there are 18 others under various stages of development."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 618740.0,
      "end_time": 621900.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 623260.0,
      "end_time": 628276.0,
      "text": "Still, most of the children who die in the United States every year"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 628300.0,
      "end_time": 630315.0,
      "text": "die in hospital rooms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 630340.0,
      "end_time": 632756.0,
      "text": "surrounded by beeping machines"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 632780.0,
      "end_time": 634876.0,
      "text": "and anxious, exhausted adults"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 634900.0,
      "end_time": 636876.0,
      "text": "who have no other option"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 636900.0,
      "end_time": 640716.0,
      "text": "but to say goodbye under those harsh, institutional lights"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 640740.0,
      "end_time": 642780.0,
      "text": "and among virtual strangers."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 643620.0,
      "end_time": 645756.0,
      "text": "For comparison&#39;s sake,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 645780.0,
      "end_time": 647116.0,
      "text": "the United Kingdom,"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 647140.0,
      "end_time": 651276.0,
      "text": "which is a country with about one fifth the population of the United States,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 651300.0,
      "end_time": 654915.0,
      "text": "and about half the size of the state of California,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 654940.0,
      "end_time": 659340.0,
      "text": "has 54 hospice and respite centers."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 661660.0,
      "end_time": 663516.0,
      "text": "Why is that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 663540.0,
      "end_time": 668315.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve asked myself that question obviously many times."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 668340.0,
      "end_time": 673836.0,
      "text": "My best guess is that Americans, with our positive can-do attitude"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 673860.0,
      "end_time": 678436.0,
      "text": "hold the expectation that our medical care system will fix it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 678460.0,
      "end_time": 682940.0,
      "text": "even though it may be a childhood illness for which there is no cure."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 683580.0,
      "end_time": 687676.0,
      "text": "We go to extraordinary measures to keep children alive"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 687700.0,
      "end_time": 691760.0,
      "text": "when in fact the greatest kindness that we might give them"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 691100.0,
      "end_time": 693836.0,
      "text": "would be a peaceful, pain-free"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 693860.0,
      "end_time": 695600.0,
      "text": "end of life."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 696220.0,
      "end_time": 699360.0,
      "text": "The transition from cure to care"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 699600.0,
      "end_time": 702276.0,
      "text": "remains a challenging one for many hospital physicians"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 702300.0,
      "end_time": 705795.0,
      "text": "whose training has really been about saving lives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 705820.0,
      "end_time": 709420.0,
      "text": "not about gently guiding the patient to the end of life."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 710460.0,
      "end_time": 713996.0,
      "text": "The dad of a sweet baby for whom we cared at the end of her life"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 714200.0,
      "end_time": 716555.0,
      "text": "certainly captured this dichotomy"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 716580.0,
      "end_time": 718156.0,
      "text": "when he reflected"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 718180.0,
      "end_time": 722156.0,
      "text": "that there are a lot of people to help you bring an infant into the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 722180.0,
      "end_time": 725579.0,
      "text": "but very few to help you usher a baby out."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 726940.0,
      "end_time": 730200.0,
      "text": "So what is the magic ingredient at George Mark?"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 730980.0,
      "end_time": 735760.0,
      "text": "The complex medical diagnoses that bring our young patients to us"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 735100.0,
      "end_time": 738760.0,
      "text": "mean that their lives have often been restricted,"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 738100.0,
      "end_time": 740836.0,
      "text": "some to a hospital bed for long periods of time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 740860.0,
      "end_time": 742716.0,
      "text": "others to wheelchairs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 742740.0,
      "end_time": 747980.0,
      "text": "still others to intensive courses of chemotherapy or rehab."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 748940.0,
      "end_time": 752636.0,
      "text": "We make a practice of ignoring those limitations."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 752660.0,
      "end_time": 754876.0,
      "text": "Our default answer is \"yes\""
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 754900.0,
      "end_time": 757660.0,
      "text": "and our default question is, \"Why not?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 758300.0,
      "end_time": 760116.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s why we took a young boy"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 760140.0,
      "end_time": 763116.0,
      "text": "who wasn&#39;t going to live for another baseball season"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 763140.0,
      "end_time": 765699.0,
      "text": "to Game 5 of the World Series."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 766580.0,
      "end_time": 769996.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s why we have a talent show put on by the staff and kids"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 770200.0,
      "end_time": 771636.0,
      "text": "for family and friends."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 771660.0,
      "end_time": 776716.0,
      "text": "Who wouldn&#39;t be enchanted by a young boy playing a piano piece with his feet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 776740.0,
      "end_time": 778260.0,
      "text": "because his arms are atrophied?"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 779620.0,
      "end_time": 781860.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s why we have a prom every year."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 783620.0,
      "end_time": 785200.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s pretty magical."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 785620.0,
      "end_time": 787476.0,
      "text": "We started the prom"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 787500.0,
      "end_time": 789116.0,
      "text": "after hearing a dad lament"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 789140.0,
      "end_time": 793620.0,
      "text": "that he would never pin a boutonniere on his son&#39;s tuxedo lapel."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 795300.0,
      "end_time": 797435.0,
      "text": "The weeks before the dance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 797460.0,
      "end_time": 798716.0,
      "text": "the house is in a flurry,"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 798740.0,
      "end_time": 801516.0,
      "text": "and I don&#39;t know who&#39;s more excited, the staff or the kids."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 801540.0,
      "end_time": 802675.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 802700.0,
      "end_time": 804316.0,
      "text": "The night of the event"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 804340.0,
      "end_time": 808796.0,
      "text": "involves rides in vintage cars,"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 808820.0,
      "end_time": 810796.0,
      "text": "a walk on a red carpet"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 810820.0,
      "end_time": 813316.0,
      "text": "into the great room,"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 813340.0,
      "end_time": 815140.0,
      "text": "a terrific DJ"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 815980.0,
      "end_time": 817756.0,
      "text": "and a photographer at the ready"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 817780.0,
      "end_time": 820315.0,
      "text": "to capture pictures of these attendees"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 820340.0,
      "end_time": 821700.0,
      "text": "and their families."
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 822460.0,
      "end_time": 824756.0,
      "text": "At the end of the evening this year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 824780.0,
      "end_time": 828459.0,
      "text": "one of our young, delightful teenaged girls,"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 829500.0,
      "end_time": 831820.0,
      "text": "Caitlin, said to her mom,"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 833460.0,
      "end_time": 836276.0,
      "text": "\"That was the best night of my whole life.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 836300.0,
      "end_time": 838675.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s just the point,"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 838700.0,
      "end_time": 842436.0,
      "text": "to capture the best days and nights,"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 842460.0,
      "end_time": 844540.0,
      "text": "to abolish limitations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 845340.0,
      "end_time": 847476.0,
      "text": "to have your default answer be \"yes\""
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 847500.0,
      "end_time": 850540.0,
      "text": "and your default question be, \"Why not?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 851620.0,
      "end_time": 854116.0,
      "text": "Ultimately life is too short,"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 854140.0,
      "end_time": 857596.0,
      "text": "whether we live to be 85 years or just eight."
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 857620.0,
      "end_time": 858876.0,
      "text": "Trust me."
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 858900.0,
      "end_time": 860740.0,
      "text": "Better yet, trust Sam."
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 862580.0,
      "end_time": 866676.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not by pretending that death doesn&#39;t exist"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 866700.0,
      "end_time": 868516.0,
      "text": "that we keep the people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 868540.0,
      "end_time": 870956.0,
      "text": "especially the little people that we love,"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 870980.0,
      "end_time": 872180.0,
      "text": "safe."
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 872900.0,
      "end_time": 874435.0,
      "text": "In the end,"
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 874460.0,
      "end_time": 877676.0,
      "text": "we can&#39;t control how long any of us lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 877700.0,
      "end_time": 879436.0,
      "text": "What we can control"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 879460.0,
      "end_time": 882760.0,
      "text": "is how we spend our days,"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 882100.0,
      "end_time": 883820.0,
      "text": "the spaces we create,"
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 884940.0,
      "end_time": 888180.0,
      "text": "the meaning and joy that we make."
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 888740.0,
      "end_time": 891756.0,
      "text": "We cannot change the outcome,"
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 891780.0,
      "end_time": 893699.0,
      "text": "but we can change the journey."
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 895500.0,
      "end_time": 896940.0,
      "text": "Isn&#39;t it time"
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 898820.0,
      "end_time": 901760.0,
      "text": "to recognize that children deserve"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 901100.0,
      "end_time": 905476.0,
      "text": "nothing less than our most uncompromising bravery"
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 905500.0,
      "end_time": 907860.0,
      "text": "and our wildest imagination."
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 908860.0,
      "end_time": 910760.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 910100.0,
      "end_time": 913660.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}